Description: Ecological niche model estimation using elipses under an M hypothesis.
    Methods for the optimization of ellipses parameter are as described in :
    Jimenez et al. (2022) <doi:10.1016/j.ecolmodel.2021.109823>.
    Critical C++ loops (Mahalanobis distance accumulation and KDE evaluation)
    are parallelised with OpenMP when available, and a simple in-memory cache
    avoids recomputing KDE bandwidths for a fixed background sample during
    likelihood optimisation.
